Install Dependencies:

bashnpm install

Create PostgreSQL Database:

bashcreatedb performance_review

Run the Schema:

bashpsql -U postgres -d performance_review -f schema.sql

Configure Environment:
Create .env file with your database credentials (see package.json artifact)
Start Server:

bashnpm run dev
ðŸ“Š Performance Scoring Formula
The system calculates scores automatically:

60% from goal completion
40% from manager feedback ratings

ðŸ”— Connect to Frontend
Update your React frontend to use these endpoints:
javascript
const API_BASE_URL = 'http://localhost:3000/api';

// Login example
const response = await fetch(`${API_BASE_URL}/auth/login`, {
  method: 'POST',
  headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' },
  body: JSON.stringify({ email, password })
});

// Protected endpoint example
const goalsResponse = await fetch(`${API_BASE_URL}/goals`, {
  headers: { 
    'Authorization': `Bearer ${token}` 
  }
});